<ITEM><HI>Good</HI> women reflect honour on all tho&s;e who had any hand in their education, and on the company they keep, i. 50. A good woman is one of the greate&s;t glories of the creation, ii. 279.&mdash;iii. 133. <HI>See al&s;o</HI> iii. 11.&mdash;vi. 295, &amp; alibi.</ITEM>
