<ITEM>Holles, Mi&s;s KITTY and PATTY, daughters of Sir John, their characters from Lady G. v. 72. Gue&s;ts at Sir Charles Grandi&s;on's nuptials, vi. 306. 312. 320. Cannot think of marrying, after having &s;een his graceful behaviour to his Lady, vi. 348. By their frequent vi&s;its, declare their admiration of him, vii. 4. Mi&s;s Patty Holles addre&s;&s;ed by Mr. James Selby, vii. 270. Mi&s;s Kitty by ano|ther Lover, ibid.</ITEM>
