<ITEM>SEBASTIANO, <HI>Signor,</HI> nephew of the Marquis of that name, pre&s;ent at the &s;olemn leave Mr. Grandi&s;on took of the family, iii. 334. Invited, with his brother Juliano, by Mr. Grandi&s;on, to England, iii. 341. They both lament that Mr. Grandi&s;on cannot be their relation, iii. 345. Vi&s;it Mr. Grandi&s;on before he quits Bologna, iii. 355. They accompany the Count of Belvedere to England, vii. 101. 155. 157. Signor Seba&s;tiano vi&s;its Lady Grandi&s;on, vii. 157. His character, from her, vii. 158. 161. 164. Lady Clemen|tina's addre&s;s to him and the Count, on their taking leave of her, vii. 286.</ITEM>
